21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係想加陣份工番一年之後就去考機電署<br />\n加陣番左2個月就黎悶死，做d野又千篇一律"},{"pid":"791bfd85878e9e6771137be8aa62493923f0dc2b","tid":437422,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"用青春換取金錢。。。。"},{"pid":"6cbefdd7e2c18893f950217bd69c211dee0bd900","tid":437422,"uid":32089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"返工頭個一個星期係齋坐架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你又要等人教你野 pw個d又未齊 係咁架喎"},{"pid":"572b22785aa27a32c290d91506d47dae0f282caf","tid":437422,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工頭個一個星期係齋坐架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你又要等人教你野 pw個d又未齊 係咁架喎</blockquote><br />\n我慘到連電腦都未有<br />\n唔知可以做咩"},{"pid":"47cc23d7e8cca4c10d5a8fa1f6f907c973af9c4e","tid":437422,"uid":125909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"覺啊...日日做到無停手，但似係消耗緊自己青春，無嘢學到，人工又唔係高，但係就老奉要ot"}]}